{"tid":806881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛上sp好痛苦","createTime":"2018-09-05T05:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T07:28:42.000Z","uid":206720,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1564d01162f14f875a12e03819943ab57f92b9f7","tid":806881,"uid":206720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"我同佢床上真係配合得天衣無縫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開頭佢講到自己好沉船咁<br />\n佢有叫過我做佢女朋友2次，唔知佢係講笑定認真啦<br />\n但2次我都未準備好所以拒絕咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近我發現自己愛上咗佢<br />\n好想用女朋友既身分照顧同呵護佢<br />\n試過同佢表白<br />\n但佢諸多藉口話咩俾唔到幸福我<br />\n<br />\n我係咪已經錯失咗個時機喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解做sp咁易沉船架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明一開頭好開心<br />\n而家就好傷心好痛苦"},{"pid":"4c7b17750c26a7864dc153e9a9379719c8fa2695","tid":806881,"uid":165499,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"臭雞 仆街死啦"},{"pid":"91aed124809857485ec6d49a21eb1440fc87333d","tid":806881,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"無人會真心鍾意雞, 仲要係免費雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b57dfd7c5b5726ccf89c3e9a07c92e5121b1fb","tid":806881,"uid":193476,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1564d01162f14f875a12e03819943ab57f92b9f7","tid":806881,"uid":206720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"我同佢床上真係配合得天衣無縫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開頭佢講到自己好沉船咁<br />\n佢有叫過我做佢女朋友2次，唔知佢係講笑定認真啦<br />\n但2次我都未準備好所以拒絕咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"